<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-262] In the PDF output, some section titles are not printed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-262</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the PDF output, all the section titles with a &apos;condition&apos; attribute are not printed. (See section 3.2.2)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To resolve this problem I use the attached &quot;customstyle_fo.xsl&quot; file.&lt;br/&gt;
I tried:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;to resolve this bug;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;to change the style of text highlighting in a way similar to html version and fix the bug &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-243&quot; title=&quot;Version tags in Lustre manual obstruct the text&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LUDOC-243&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LUDOC-243&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; that continues to be present in 28.4.1.1.3 or 33.4;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;to add the automatic line wrapping in monospace.verbatim environment (partially solving the bug-60).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
